Pierre Collins was taken into custody on suspicion of second-degree murder in the death of Barway Collins . 
  The body of the 10-year-old was found in the Mississippi River on Saturday . 
  Police Chief Stephanie Revering said the boy's father is a primary suspect in the case . 
  Barway was last seen on March 18 and his father has said he is innocent . 
  Mr Collins appeared at a vigil for his son last month . 
 